    <p class="description">AIOSEO is the second-most-installed WordPress SEO plugin (3M+ active installs) with the cleanest setup wizard in the category. It also <strong>locks features behind paid tiers that RankMath gives away for free</strong>. After 30 days of testing both side by side, here is the honest 2026 verdict.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
