    <div class="post-grid">
      <article class="post-content">
        <p class="lede-p"><strong>AIOSEO is the best onboarding experience in the WordPress SEO plugin category.</strong> It is also the priciest of the major three (AIOSEO, RankMath, Yoast) once you need schema, local, and redirects — features RankMath bundles into its free tier. After 30 days of side-by-side testing and interviews with 11 paying customers, here is the honest verdict and the real total monthly cost of running SEO on WordPress in 2026.</p>

