          <div class="callout-label">⚡ TL;DR — The 30-second verdict</div>
          <p><strong>Buy AIOSEO if</strong> you are on WordPress, want the cleanest setup experience, and need reliable on-page SEO configuration. Pro tier ($199/yr) is the sweet spot — it includes schema, local SEO, and redirects. <strong>Skip AIOSEO if</strong> you are budget-sensitive (RankMath's free tier covers most needs) or if you need content produced rather than configured. The plugin does not write a word. If you want traffic without learning WordPress SEO, theStacc handles writing, publishing, and ranks from $99/mo.</p>
        </div>

