            <div class="cc-row"><span>Writers — ~30 articles @ $80 each</span><strong>$2,400</strong></div>
            <div class="cc-row"><span>Editor + project management</span><strong>$1,500</strong></div>
            <div class="cc-row cc-row-total"><span>What you actually spend</span><strong>$4,165 /mo</strong></div>
          </div>
          <div class="cc-vs">
            <span class="cc-vs-label">VS theStacc</span>
            <div class="cc-vs-row">
              <span>theStacc Bundle — all three modules, done for you</span>
