        <h3>Probably not the right call</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Budget-sensitive owners (RankMath free covers most needs)</li>
          <li>Sites on Webflow, Ghost, Shopify, or headless CMSes</li>
          <li>Owners who need content <em>produced</em>, not configured</li>
          <li>Anyone wanting rank tracking, keyword research, or backlink data inside the plugin</li>
